{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0171or8tuBAMTNuu4D5KCz9Y","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have gathered all the necessary information. Let me compile my comprehensive report with all findings:\n\n## Research Findings Report\n\nI've successfully researched all the requested items in your Go Cloche project. Here are the complete findings:\n\n### 1. Design Document: `/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-project-versioning-design.md`\n\nThis document details a project versioning system with these key specifications:\n\n**Version File:**\n- Location: `.cloche/version`\n- Content: Single decimal integer followed by newline (e.g., `3\\n`)\n- Created by `cloche init` with initial value `1`\n- NOT gitignored — should be committed to git\n\n**Increment Rule:**\n- In `internal/evolution/orchestrator.go`, after Stage 5 (Audit), check if `len(result.Changes) > 0`\n- If true, call `incrementProjectVersion(o.cfg.ProjectDir)`\n- If file doesn't exist, treat as implicit version 1 and write `2`\n\n**Read Path:**\n- New function: `config.LoadVersion(projectDir string) (int, error)` \n- Returns integer from `.cloche/version`, defaults to `1` if missing\n\n**Surface:**\n- `/api/projects/{name}/info` endpoint displays version as `v3`\n- Evolution audit log already records `ChangesJSON` separately\n\n**Required Changes:**\n1. `internal/evolution/orchestrator.go` — Call `incrementProjectVersion` after changes detected\n2. `internal/config/config.go` — Add `LoadVersion()` and `incrementProjectVersion()` (unexported)\n3. `cmd/cloche/init.go` — Write `.cloche/version` with content `1\\n`\n4. `internal/adapters/web/handler.go` — Include version in `/api/projects/{name}/info` response\n\n---\n\n### 2. Existing `cloche init` Implementation: `/workspace/cmd/cloche/init.go`\n\n**Key Features:**\n- Command: `cmdInit(args []string)` function\n- Already includes version file creation at line 195: `{filepath.Join(clocheDir, \"version\"), versionContent, 0644}`\n- `versionContent = \"1\\n\"` (defined at line 106)\n\n**Files Created by Init:**\n- Workflow file: `.cloche/{workflow-name}.cloche`\n- Dockerfile: `.cloche/Dockerfile`\n- Config: `.cloche/config.toml`\n- Prompts: `.cloche/prompts/{implement,fix,update-docs}.md`\n- **Version file:** `.cloche/version` (already implemented!)\n- Host workflow: `.cloche/host.cloche`\n- Script: `.cloche/scripts/prepare-prompt.sh`\n\n**Gitignore Management:**\n- Uses `removeGitignoreEntries()` and `addGitignoreEntries()` helpers\n- Already handles version file creation with proper skipping if exists\n\n---\n\n### 3. Evolution Orchestrator: `/workspace/internal/evolution/orchestrator.go`\n\n**Current State:**\n- Lines 1-121: Defines `OrchestratorConfig` with ProjectDir, WorkflowName, LLM, MinConfidence\n- `Orchestrator` struct wires all evolution pipeline stages\n- `Run()` method executes 5 stages:\n  1. **Collect** — gathers run data\n  2. **Classify** — classifies triggering run\n  3. **Reflect** — generates lessons\n  4. **Execute** — handles \"prompt_improvement\" and \"new_step\" lessons (lines 84-99)\n  5. **Audit** — logs and saves evolution (lines 101-118)\n\n**Current Result Structure:**\n- `result.Changes` is populated when lessons are applied (lines 92, 131, 190)\n- After audit at line 104, result is saved to store (lines 107-118)\n- **Missing:** No `incrementProjectVersion()` call (design expects it here after line 104)\n\n---\n\n### 4. API Handler for Project Info: `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler.go`\n\n**Handler: `handleAPIProjectInfo`** (lines 939-1025)\n\n**Current Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"docker_image\": \"...\",\n  \"version\": 0,\n  \"prompt_files\": [...]\n}\n```\n\n**Key Implementation Details:**\n- Line 962-968: Reads `.cloche/version` and parses as integer (defaults to 0 if missing)\n- Uses `strconv.Atoi()` to parse version\n- Extracts Docker image from Dockerfile FROM line (lines 945-959)\n- Collects prompt file history using `git log` (lines 970-1017)\n\n**Endpoint Route:** `GET /api/projects/{name}/info` (line 153)\n\n**Current State:** Version reading is already partially implemented but stores 0 as default instead of 1\n\n---\n\n### 5. .gitignore File: `/workspace/.gitignore`\n\n**Version-Related Entries:**\n- `.cloche/version` is NOT listed (correct per design)\n- Entries that ARE gitignored:\n  - `.cloche/*-*-*/` — runtime directories\n  - `.cloche/run-*/` — run artifacts\n  - `.cloche/attempt_count/`\n  - `.cloche/evolution/`\n  - `.cloche/history.log`\n  - `.cloche/prompt.txt`\n  - `.cloche/output/`\n\n**Key Point:** Config/workflow/prompt files are tracked; runtime artifacts are not.\n\n---\n\n### 6. Config Package: `/workspace/internal/config/config.go`\n\n**Current Structure:**\n- Three config types: `DaemonConfig`, `EvolutionConfig`, `OrchestrationConfig`\n- All wrapped in `Config` struct\n- Functions: `Load()`, `LoadGlobal()`, `LoadGlobalFrom()`\n\n**Evolution Config Fields:**\n- `Enabled` (bool)\n- `DebounceSeconds` (int)\n- `MinConfidence` (string)\n- `MaxPromptBullets` (int)\n\n**Orchestration Config Fields:**\n- `Enabled` (bool)\n- `Tracker` (string)\n- `Concurrency` (int)\n- `Workflow` (string)\n\n**Missing Functions:**\n- `LoadVersion(projectDir string) (int, error)` — needs to be added\n- `incrementProjectVersion(projectDir string)` — needs to be added (unexported helper)\n\n**Test Coverage:** `/workspace/internal/config/config_test.go` contains comprehensive tests for all config types\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Implementation Status\n\n| Item | Status | Notes |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| Version file concept | Design ✓ | Fully specified in design doc |\n| `cloche init` creates version | Already ✓ | Line 195 in init.go |\n| Evolution calls increment | Missing | Needs addition after line 104 in evolution/orchestrator.go |\n| `config.LoadVersion()` | Missing | Needs to be added to config.go |\n| `incrementProjectVersion()` | Missing | Needs to be added to config.go